org.jnosql.diana.api.key

Interface BucketManagerFactory<T extends BucketManager>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, CloseResource

    public interface BucketManagerFactory<T extends BucketManager>
extends CloseResource
    BucketManager factory. When the application has finished using the bucket manager factory, and/or at application shutdown, the application should close the column family manager factory.
